nodes.text: Kiki was a type of food eaten the Unknown Regions of the galaxy that was composed of red, orange, and pale-blue half moons. While onboard the ship of Yiv the Benevolent, Mitth'raw'nuruodo and Qilori of Uandualon noted a dish of kiki, which the latter advised Thrawn not to eat, as digesting it required specialized digestive juices.
